<exercise checkit-seed="0003" checkit-slug="P5" checkit-title="Expected Value">
    <statement>
        
                <p>
                    A restaurant offers a grab bag of 23 fortune cookies, 4 of them have a discount of \$5 in them, 13 of them have a \$1 discount, and the rest have merely fortunes in them. If Nuriyah grabs one at random, what is the expected value of the draw?
                </p> 
    </statement>
    <answer>
        <p>
            The expected value is <m>\frac{4}{23}(5) + \frac{13}{23}(1) + 0 = $1.43</m>
        </p>
    </answer>
</exercise>
